    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Books of tropes, which are introductions to liturgical chants or interpolations or elaborations to the text of the Catholic Mass. They were discontinued when the Roman Missal was revised under Pius V (1566-1572).</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000099620/Legacy AAT data</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Libros de tropos, que son introducciones a los cantos litúrgicos o interpolaciones o elaboraciones al texto de la Misa Católica. Se discontinuaron cuando el Misal Romano fue revisado bajo el mandato del Papa Pío V (1566-1572).</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051034/TAA database (2000-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Boeken met tropen, dat wil zeggen inleidingen op liturgische gezangen of interpolaties en uitwerkingen van de tekst van de katholieke mis. Ze werden gebruikt totdat het Roomse misboek onder paus Pius V (1566-1572) werd herzien.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>文學轉喻之書，作為教會詩歌的入門曲，或天主教彌撒經文的竄改或註釋。但於羅馬聖庇護五世(1566-1572)將彌撒經書修改後已經失傳。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
